---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";

import kuduBull from "../assets/images/kudu-bull.jpg";
import huntKuduPair from "../assets/images/hunt-kudu-pair.jpg";
import phSunset from "../assets/images/ph-sunset.jpg";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet the Caldwell family — three generations of free-range, fair-chase hunting in South Africa, led by professional hunters Mike and Jayden Caldwell."
  overHero={true}
>
  <Hero
    image={kuduBull}
    alt="A greater kudu bull stands alert in the South African bushveld"
    kicker="Since 1993"
    heading="A family, a legacy,<br>a track through Africa."
    sub="Meet the Caldwells — the people behind every safari."
    compact={true}
  />

  <Section variant="sand">
    <div class="container--narrow text-center stack">
      <span class="kicker">Our story</span>
      <h2>Respect for the wild, passed down a generation.</h2>
      <p class="lede">For the Caldwells, hunting has always been about more than the trophy — it is about fair chase, reverence for the animal, and the quiet thrill of the stalk. This is where it began, and where it is headed.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Mike -->
  <Section variant="paper">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="split__media">
        <Image src={huntKuduPair} alt="Mike Caldwell with a heavy-horned kudu" widths={[480, 760, 1000]} sizes="(min-width:900px) 46vw, 90vw" format="avif" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="split__text stack">
        <span class="kicker">The founder</span>
        <h2>Mike Caldwell</h2>
        <p>Mike found his passion for the hunt as a boy, at his father Trevor's side in the old Eastern Transvaal — now Mpumalanga — chasing birds and small antelope across the veld. When he came of age he bought his first rifle, and a lifelong pursuit of Southern Africa's plains game began.</p>
        <p>In 1993 he turned that passion into a profession, qualifying as a professional hunter and outfitter. Caldwell Safaris was born. He went on to hunt the great trophies of Mozambique and northern Zimbabwe in pursuit of the Big&nbsp;Five — and earned a name as a respected Big&nbsp;Five outfitter.</p>
        <p>Mike and his wife Roz have shared a love of wildlife for over thirty years, raising their children — Jayden, Tristen and Tannah — with the same values they hold for the African wilderness: to respect it, and to protect it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Jayden -->
  <Section variant="sand">
    <div class="container split split--reverse">
      <div class="split__text stack">
        <span class="kicker">The future</span>
        <h2>Jayden Caldwell</h2>
        <p>From the time he could walk, Jayden was on his father's hunts — usually up on Mike's shoulders, with a bird's-eye view of the veld. He took his first animal at ten, only once he truly understood what ethical hunting means. He has never forgotten it.</p>
        <blockquote class="pull-quote">
          &ldquo;Calm and compassionate in the field, Jayden is — without fail — the part of the safari our guests remember.&rdquo;
          <cite>— Roz Caldwell</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <p>At sixteen he became an apprentice professional hunter under his father's guidance, and in time a full PH. &ldquo;He taught me not just how to be effective,&rdquo; Jayden says, &ldquo;but how to be ethical. I've taken his mantra as my own.&rdquo;</p>
      </div>
      <div class="split__media">
        <Image src={phSunset} alt="Jayden Caldwell silhouetted against a bushveld sunset" widths={[480, 760, 1000]} sizes="(min-width:900px) 46vw, 90vw" format="avif" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Ethos -->
  <Section variant="green">
    <div class="container--narrow text-center stack">
      <span class="kicker">Our ethos</span>
      <p class="mantra">&ldquo;Hunt fair, and with respect.&rdquo;</p>
      <p class="lede" style="color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--cream) 86%, transparent); margin-inline:auto;">Genuine free-range, fair-chase hunting on open country — conducted ethically, with reverence for the animal and the wild it belongs to. It is the heart of everything we do.</p>
      <div class="btn-row" style="justify-content:center; margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Plan Your Safari</a>
        <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn--outline">View the gallery</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .split { display: grid; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: center; }
  .split__media :global(img) { width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow); aspect-ratio: 4/3; object-fit: cover; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-xl); }
    .split--reverse .split__media { order: -1; }
  }
  .pull-quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--ochre);
    padding: 0.2rem 0 0.2rem var(--space-sm);
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--step-2);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .pull-quote cite { display: block; margin-top: 0.6rem; font-family: var(--font-body); font-style: normal; font-size: var(--step--1); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--bark); }
  .mantra { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--step-4); color: var(--cream); }
</style>
